BM&FBovespa to Review Strategy After Bourse Mergers, Estado Says

-- B y   L a u r a   P r i c e
-- 
2011-03-17T10:29:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-17/bm-fbovespa-to-review-strategy-after-bourse-mergers-estado-says.html
  BM&FBovespa SA (BVMF3)  is reviewing its
growth strategy because of a trend for global stock exchange
mergers and acquisitions, O Estado de S. Paulo reported, citing
Chief Executive Officer Edemir Pinto.  The Sao Paulo-based bourse will focus on developing markets
and partnerships within Latin America, Pinto told the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
